data.title: Ryan Starr - 2019-20 - Men's Basketball
data.meta_description: Ryan Starr (2) G  - 2019-20: Played and started in 25 games … Averaged 31.5 minutes per game with 787 minutes played … Scored 286 points on the year,
data.text:
2019-20: Played and started in 25 games … Averaged 31.5 minutes per game with 787 minutes played … Scored 286 points on the year, averaging 11.4 points per game … Shot 101-of-263 (.384) from the field … Shot 33-of-104 (.317) from 3-point range … Shot 51-of-61 (.836) from the free throw line … Collected 109 rebounds (2.8 per game) … Had eight blocks … Made 46 steals … Recorded 101 assists …

2018-19: Played in all 14 games off the bench … Averaged 7.4 minutes per game with 104 minutes played … Scored 14 points on the year … Shot 3-of-19 from the field … Shot 2-of-16 from 3-point range … Shot 6-of-6 from the free throw line … Collected 15 rebounds … Made eight steals … Recorded 12 assists …

Prep: Lettered three years at Northern Highlands Regional High School as a point guard … Two-time First Team All-League …
